{"article_id":"6DwhVT13Xn5HNkQj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A judge convicted former police officer Michael Slager of second-degree murder","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"and sentenced him to 20 years in prison Thursday for the 2015 killing of Walter Scott , an unarmed black motorist .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Slager ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"who is white ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"shot the 50-year-old motorist in April 2015","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"when Scott tried to run for it","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"after getting pulled over .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The ruling comes","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"after Slager changed his story of the shooting a number of times .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"He initially reported","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"\" shots fired","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and the subject is down ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he took my Taser , \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"but video of the incident showed","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that Scott had done no such thing .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"In fact , Slager walked over","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and placed his taser next to Scott ' s body","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"after calling it in .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"CHARLESTON , S.C.","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Judge rules","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"ex-South Carolina officer # MichaelSlager committed second-degree murder in the shooting of unarmed black motorist # WalterScott .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"pic.twitter.com/Q1lAfauBlF","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"- Meg Kinnard","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"( @ MegKinnardAP )","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"December 7 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"The judge spared Slager of a life sentence ,","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"as he was initially facing a first-degree murder charge .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"A bystander ' s video begins","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"with Scott and Slager both standing","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and locked in some type of struggle .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"It is unclear from the video ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"but it appears that Slager ' s Taser had been deployed .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Scott then runs away from Slager ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"at which point the officer opens fire .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"He shoots eight times ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"and Scott is seen stumbling","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"as he is hit .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"After he falls to the ground ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Slager appears to look to the side and slightly over his shoulder .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"He walks towards Scott","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"as he begins speaking into his police radio .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Slager is then heard commanding Scott to put his hands behind his back .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"He is seen cuffing Scott","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"and then walking away","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"as another officer arrives on the scene .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Slager was a five-year veteran of the force ,","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"and Scott had an outstanding arrest warrant for family court .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"His criminal record showed failures","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to pay child support ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"as well as an arrest for an undefined violent crime in 1987 .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":101,"left":68,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":57,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":52,"right":56,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":56,"left":53,"right":55,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":53,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":4,"right":54,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":5,"right":6,"relat